Symbol.Script_3D:
! VAV Reheat Water Coil
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, dTHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, dTHeight, unID: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, dTHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, dTHeight, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
ADD -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, 0 BLOCK dTWidth, dTDepth, dTHeight DEL 1
dist = 0.07*(dTHeight/0.30) alpha = 180-2*ATN((dist/2)/0.03) rr = (dist/2)/SIN(alpha)
ADD -dTWidth/2, 0, dTHeight*0.75 ROTx 90 ADDz -0.005 PRISM_ 3, 0.01, 0, dist/2, 79, rr-0.03, 0, 915, 0, -dist/2, 3015 DEL 3
ADD -dTWidth/2, 0, dTHeight/4 ROTx 90 ADDz -0.005 PRISM_ 3, 0.01, 0, dist/2, 79, rr-0.03, 0, 915, 0, -dist/2, 3015 DEL 3
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 1, ConPosX_3=ConPosX_3, ConPosY_3=ConPosY_3, ConPosZ_3=ConPosZ_3, ConLength_3=ConLength_3, ConEdit_3 = 14, ConPosX_4=ConPosX_4, ConPosY_4=ConPosY_4, ConPosZ_4=ConPosZ_4, ConLength_4=ConLength_4, ConEdit_4 = 14 END
Symbol.Script_2D:
! VAV Reheat Water Coil
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -dTWidth/2-0.03, -0.005, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -dTWidth/2-0.03, 0.005, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
PUT -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, 1, -dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, 1, dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, 1, dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, 1, -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, -1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
PUT -dTWidth/2, -0.005, 1, -dTWidth/2, 0.005, 1, -dTWidth/2-0.03, 0.005, 1, -dTWidth/2-0.03, -0.005, 1, -dTWidth/2, -0.005, -1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP) ENDIF
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 -SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED))+SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND SYMB_MIRRORED)
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 1, ConPosX_3=ConPosX_3, ConPosY_3=ConPosY_3, ConLength_3=ConLength_3, ConEdit_3 = 1, ConPosX_4=ConPosX_4, ConPosY_4=ConPosY_4, ConLength_4=ConLength_4, ConEdit_4 = 1 DEL 1
END
